data.description: Excellent cul-de-sac home site in this exciting community built in 2020.  The back yard is fenced and flat ready for all fun activities!  The 4th bedroom is very large and could be used as an upstairs family room.  The kitchen is open and inviting. Granite countertops and coordinated back splash. 2 car garage, outdoor storage shed, covered porch and deck! Maintenance is easy with the vinyl siding and attractive cultured stone accents.
